  "details": "\n---\n_-= Per source details. Do not edit below this line.=-_\n\n## Source: amazon-inspector (72ea86dd3432c899e1fac658c0474958798e1e953d4f01d8f487d692db5c07aa)\nThe package gunpowder-ghost was found to contain malicious code.\n\n## Source: ossf-package-analysis (70dc4997af7e9a6e5468ab528abef41f755038e72abee6fa9a59fcec98825e54)\nThe OpenSSF Package Analysis project identified 'gunpowder-ghost' @ 209.0.0 (npm) as malicious.\n\nIt is considered malicious because:\n\n- The package communicates with a domain associated with malicious activity.\n\n- The package executes one or more commands associated with malicious behavior.\n",
